These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bluemaster, cain
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, badminton, swimming
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, chestnut
1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the cain-smoker##1
5. the game-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking water is the cain-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage      | water  | juice       | mirinda   |
| Cigar          | cain | game | bluemaster |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | swimming | badminton    |
| Color   | chestnut | apricot       | aquamarine      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, potato, radish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, july
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, mystery, fantasy
House: farmhouse, townhouse, cottage
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the cottage house is on the far left##1
6. the cottage house is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Food          | pear      | potato  | radish        |
| Birthday         | july | september | january |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | mystery | fantasy       |
| House           | cottage     | townhouse     | farmhouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, yellow, apricot
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, december
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
House: victorian, futuristic, craftsman
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the victorian house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Color      | yellow    | blue        | apricot |
| Birthday           | january    | december | june    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| House     | craftsman     | victorian                | futuristic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, horse
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, lawyer
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, mauve, blue
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, november, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the owner of the cat is the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who likes black is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Pet          | hamster    | horse  | cat      |
| Job           | lawyer    | analyst | fisherman |
| Color   | blue   | mauve  | black     |
| Birthday   | december | november    | march      |

