.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: snooker, poker, scrabble
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis, dahlia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, superhero
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, parkour, skiing
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is the person playing snooker##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person who growslily##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game         | scrabble | snooker     | poker   |
| Flower           | dahlia       | amaryllis   | lily     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | documentary | superhero |
| Sport           | skiing      | handball         | parkour  |

