.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, horror, animation
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, colombian
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine, ivory
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1
3. the colombian is on the far left##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre          | superhero | horror       | animation |
| Nationality   | colombian     | chinese       | indonesian   |
| Color           | aquamarine      | yellow       | ivory     |
| Sport         | sailing   | snowboarding | tennis  |

