.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, snowmobile
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, police-officer
City: miami, hannover, new-york
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bluemaster, montecristo
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Transport          | snowmobile       | quad-bike         | taxi   |
| Job           | accountant | police-officer | dressmaker |
| City   | miami     | hannover        | new-york        |
| Cigar   | bluemaster      | aristoff           | montecristo        |

