.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, badminton, baseball
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, turquise, chestnut
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, april, july
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | soccer | baseball         | badminton       |
| Color           | red      | chestnut      | turquise         |
| Birthday     | april      | july         | october          |

