.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, handball, lacrosse
City: edinburgh, liverpool, london
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince, aristoff
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Sport       | handball            | badminton      | lacrosse  |
| City         | london | edinburgh | liverpool |
| Cigar         | dannemann               | aristoff | prince |
| Transport   | roller             | ship       | bus      |

