The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, june
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, orchid
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, lemonade
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the electrician is on the far right##1
5. the chef is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | chef         | electrician |
| Birthday   | may      | march | june     |
| Flower   | poppy   | marigold       | orchid     |
| Beverage           | lemonade    | tea         | milk        |

