.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, light-blue, red
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall, prince
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, thai
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, sprite
1. the thai is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the person who likes red##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Color           | light-blue | red | turquise |
| Cigar   | prince        | pall-mall       | cain     |
| Nationality   | french     | thai         | dutch     |
| Beverage     | sprite | fanta          | soy-milk      |

