.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, writing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, sunflower
3 different games are played: snooker, canasta, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | cooking | writing   |
| Flower           | sunflower     | tulip    | marigold   |
| Game   | canasta         | whist    | snooker   |
| Transport         | skateboard       | bike | ship |

