.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
City: berlin, hannover, colone
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, strawberry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, rugby, cricket
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, manager, dancer
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the librarian##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the person traveling to colone is the dancer##1
6. the manager is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| City    | berlin | hannover     | colone      |
| Food        | garlic | lime       | strawberry |
| Sport       | rugby | water-polo | cricket  |
| Job   | manager    | librarian   | dancer  |

