3 different pets are kept: pony, goat, hedgehog
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the owner of the goat is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
6. the person eating peas is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower      | balloon-flower | iris | sunflower       |
| Food          | peas     | artichoke   | kale       |
| Movie-Genre         | sports  | animation   | western |
| Pet   | goat   | hedgehog       | pony  |

