3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | milk    | cola    |
