3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
