The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, mauvecher
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who growsmauvecher is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who likes mauve is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person driving the bus is the person who likes purple##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Color      | purple         | mauve     | brown     |
| Flower           | daisy        | mauvecher | lily |
| Transport   | bus        | snowmobile   | bike    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby   | water-polo |

