.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, bus
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, dahlia, daisy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, r&b
House: colonial, futuristic, ranch-style
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the colonial house is on the far left##1
5. the futuristic house is in the middle##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Transport          | bus     | boat    | skateboard    |
| Flower         | tulip | daisy | dahlia     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | folk      | r&b        |
| House         | colonial   | futuristic   | ranch-style |

 